    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/d26f839dc6835da6de2cc576e0b56617.poster.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1040 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/d26f839dc6835da6de2cc576e0b56617.webm?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/d26f839dc6835da6de2cc576e0b56617.mp4?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Tale of LUMI</strong> 是一款受 <strong>类银河战士恶魔城（Metroidvania）</strong> 启发的2D动作游戏。你将扮演 <strong>Atlas</strong>，踏上重建被毁灭的 <strong>LUMI</strong> 王国的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集 <strong>神赐之力（GODLY POWERUPS）</strong>，击败 <strong>强大的敌人</strong>，解开 <strong>引人入胜的谜题</strong>，<strong>提升</strong> 自身技能，并 <strong>探索</strong> 与 <strong>重建</strong> 陨落的 <strong>LUMI</strong> 王国！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/4aa793d28b3af74979848000efbcf350.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1041 height=131 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/101a1454159e7b7b0cf65a94a8d04c30.poster.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/101a1454159e7b7b0cf65a94a8d04c30.webm?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/101a1454159e7b7b0cf65a94a8d04c30.mp4?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经的 <strong>LUMI</strong> 王国守护着世界间的连接，象征着希望。直到在 <strong>全日食</strong> 之时，<strong>Nightbringers</strong> 唤醒了原初之神 <strong>Khaos</strong>，使这片曾经辉煌的土地化为废墟。<strong>探索</strong> 这片堕落的王国及其隐藏的秘密，通过与 <strong>强大的存在</strong> 互动，解锁整个地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/306446503058be6c3ca19b690b879ac5.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1041 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/4c4348b02dd399dddbec4848fcbd2a93.poster.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/4c4348b02dd399dddbec4848fcbd2a93.webm?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/4c4348b02dd399dddbec4848fcbd2a93.mp4?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/648de6f8840389f138d9c2ff4fcc1cd7.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1041 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险过程中，你将收集 <strong>神赐之力</strong>。这些力量赋予你独特的能力，帮助你解谜、探索地图并击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/a528db17867c79d1af13f128b71fac61.poster.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/a528db17867c79d1af13f128b71fac61.webm?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/a528db17867c79d1af13f128b71fac61.mp4?t=1770816320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着 <strong>Atlas</strong> 在王国中不断深入，<strong>强化</strong> 与 <strong>升级</strong> 你的 <strong>神赐之力</strong>，迎接 <strong>Nightbringers</strong> 与 <strong>Khaos</strong> 带来的终极挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334400/extras/1a40ac8b7c1b656c3c7ead4817241276.avif?t=1770816320\" width=1232 height=404 /></span></p>",
